     <text:p text:style-name="P52"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#c10_Considerations_sur_la_France___edition_1829_X.xhtml#cite_ref-3-n295" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition">↑</text:span></text:a> </text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T14">Scimus, et hanc veniam petimusque damusque vicissim ;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14">Sed non ut placidis coeant immitia, non ut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14">Serpentes avibus geminentur, tigribus agni.</text:span></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P52">C’est ce que certains cabinets peuvent dire de mieux à l’Europe qui les interroge.</text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P52"/>
