     <text:p text:style-name="P78"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#c0_Lettres_a_un_gentilhomme_russe_sur_l_inquisition_espagnole.xhtml#cite_ref-p182_111-0" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="Definition"><text:span text:style-name="T6">↑</text:span></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T6"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">I have endeavoured to open the eyes of the public ; if I live a few years longer I may have the satisfaction of seeing the down-fall of some of the prevailing systems of superstition.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"> Ibid., pag. 11.</text:span></text:p>
